## üìã **Standard Workflows**

### **1. Starting New Work**
```python
# Check current status first
mcp_git_git_status(repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs")

# Create Linear task and get NMSTX-XX ID
linear_create_issue(...)  # Returns issue with ID

# Create branch with Linear ID
mcp_git_git_create_branch(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    branch_name="NMSTX-XX-feature-description",
    base_branch="main"  # or current branch
)

# Switch to new branch
mcp_git_git_checkout(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    branch_name="NMSTX-XX-feature-description"
)
```

### **2. Making Changes**
```python
# Check what changed
mcp_git_git_diff_unstaged(repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs")

# Stage specific files
mcp_git_git_add(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    files=["src/agents/simple/new_agent.py", "tests/test_new_agent.py"]
)

# Review staged changes
mcp_git_git_diff_staged(repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs")

# Commit with semantic message
mcp_git_git_commit(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    message="feat(NMSTX-XX): implement new agent functionality"
)
```

### **3. Incremental Commits**
```python
# After each subtask completion
mcp_git_git_add(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    files=["src/file.py"]
)

mcp_git_git_commit(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    message="feat(NMSTX-XX): complete agent initialization"
)

# Continue with next subtask...
mcp_git_git_commit(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    message="test(NMSTX-XX): add unit tests for agent"
)
```

### **4. Pushing Changes**
```python
# MCP doesn't support push, use terminal
run_terminal_cmd(
    command="git push origin NMSTX-XX-feature-description",
    is_background=False
)
```

### **5. Reviewing History**
```python
# View recent commits
mcp_git_git_log(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    max_count=10
)

# Show specific commit
mcp_git_git_show(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    revision="HEAD"  # or commit hash
)

# Compare with main branch
mcp_git_git_diff(
    repo_path="/root/prod/am-agents-labs",
    target="origin/main"
)
```

